    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>orzo pasta</strong> and 900ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.8L]<strong> </span>boiled water </strong>to the pot<strong> </strong>with the<strong> chicken stock mix </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Bring to the boil then reduce the heat to medium-high</p>",
