    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>shredded spring greens</strong> and <strong>pork meatballs</strong> to the pot</p><p>Cook for 12-15 min or until the meatballs are cooked through (no pink meat!) and the orzo is cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Tip: Stir the orzo occasionally to stop it from sticking</p>",
